<a href="http://www.panapress.com/Nigeria-to-ban-rice-importation-in-2014--13-880759-0-lang1-index.html" target="_self">http://www.panapress.com/Nigeria-to-ban-rice-importation-in-2014--13-880...</a></p><p><i>Oryza.com</i>, ‘Nigeria bans rice imports via land to curb smuggling’, 7 May 2013</p><p>
